data.text:
@paulieok @kevinhunt101 Hello Paul,
We apologize for the canceled flight and all the inconveniences caused by the situation. In order for the situation to be verified, we kindly request that you please fill in the available claim form, through our website's contacts page. (1/2)
@HarshilRulez You are welcome ✈️ please let us know if you have any other questions. Thank you

@morgs__87 Hello Morgan,
We will answer to your private message as soon as possible. Thank you for understanding
@bwings80 Hi! We deeply regret the situation. To better assist you, please DM us your booking reference or electronic ticket number. Thank you in advance.

@wildlyartistic Should there be anything else we can help you with at the moment, please let us know. Also, if you need any assistance, we are also available to help you through this channel. Thank you for understanding. (2/2)
@Christian160257 Bonsoir! Nous vous remercions pour votre retour. N'hésitez pas à revenir vers nous si besoin. Merci d'avance.

@noeffingcluex Hello me,

can you inform us through DM your booking reference or electronic ticket number (047...) so we may verify? Thank you.

@doart3 @ageekymom Hello Duarte,

can you inform us through DM your TAP Miles & Go and email address related so we may verify? Thank you.

@ageekymom Hello Lisa,
May you please let us know your TAP client number or your email address via DM?

@HarshilRulez Alright, we understand and apologize for the situation, as it is required for the online check-in to be completed with a valid document. Nevertheless, we inform you that you may also do it directly at the airport instead. Thank you

@epilefandrade Olá Felipe,

os valores poderão variar consoante a disponibilidade tarifária. Não existe forma de garantir que um valor que verifique num determinado dia, se matenha mais tarda. Obrigado.
@aicela__ Hi! We have replied to your DM. Thank you in advance.

@jules_foreva Hi! We inform you that if the lowest bid is over £100 per person, you will not be able to offer less than that. Your offer will not be accepted in this case. Feel free to contact us, if you have any other questions. Thank you in advance.

@ShaunRoden29 Hi! We deeply regret the situation. We inform you that your case is still under review. We will update you once we have more details. We appreciate your patience at this time. Thank you in advance.
@SallyCo39652616 Hi! To better assist you, please DM us your claim number as well as the email address linked to it. Thank you in advance.

@alluneediz1mik3 Hi! We inform you that your case is still under review. We will update you once there is further information available. We appreciate your patience at this time. Thank you in advance.

@TravelBee10 Hello TravelBee,
We apologize for the situation. Please let us know how to assist you through this channel. Thank you
@fred_bout Hi! We have replied to your request via DM. Thank you in advance.

@Eri_prezi Olá! Lamentamos a situação reportada. Informamos que respondemos à mensagem que nos enviou via Instagram. De futuro e de forma a evitar duplicações, sugerimos que utilize apenas um canal de contacto. Ficamos ao dispor para qualquer esclarecimento adicional. Obrigada.

@GusLoze Bonsoir Guillaume, 
Pouvez-vous nos envoyer les informations de votre hospitalisation par message privé? De document qui l'atteste. Merci

@_jimdw_ Hello Jim,
May you please let us know your ticket number or your complaint number via DM so we may verify your case? Thank you.

@senriquebh Olá Sérgio,

poderia nos indicar, por mensagem privada, o seu código de reserva ou número de bilhete eletrónico (047...), bem como o laudo médico, para que possamos verificar, por favor? Obrigado.
@HarshilRulez Therefore, we request that you check with the responsible authorities if you can travel with another document or not. Please let us know if you have any other questions. Thank you (2/2)

@HarshilRulez Danger-zone,
We inform you that you must change the document previously to the flight departure as you will be obliged to present it in order to be able to travel.  (1/2)

@giberelina Olá Clarissa,
Para que seja possível verificar, sugerimos que nos indique o seu código de reserva. 
Por razões de confidencialidade de dados, sugerimos o envio dos mesmos através de DM.
Obrigada.
@pmigabreu Olá Pedro, qual o código de reserva ou número de bilhete eletrónico? Sugerimos os dados por mensagem privada por razões de confidencialidade. Obrigado.
@lyracMVS Hi lyrac, can you please send us a print of the error that you're receiving? We suggest the details through DM. Thank you

@Fabricio_jun10 Olá Fabricio,
Respondemos à sua mensagem privada.  
Permanecemos ao dispor. 
Obrigado.

@GusLoze Bonjour Guillaume, afin de vérifier la situation, nous vous demandons de bien vouloir nous indiquer le code de votre réservation ou le numéro du billet électronique. Pour des raisons de sécurité, veuillez nous envoyer l'information par message privé. Merci.

@huchkultur Hello Huchkultur,
in order to verify the status of your process, please provide us with the number of the case and e-mail address associated. 
For confidentiality reasons, we suggest you to send the details by private message.
Thank you.

@mrworldview Hello Alex,
first of all, please accept our sincere apologies for the waiting.
We will verify your case and you will be contacted by e-mail as soon as possible.
We thank you for your understanding and we remain available for any other questions.
@jgeremia For confidential reasons, we suggest you to send this information through DM.

@KalpeshMorarji @OurmieresChris Hello Kalpesh,
once again, please accept our sincere apologies for the waiting. Rest assured that our teams are handling your case and you will be contacted as soon as possible. We appreciate your patience at this time. Thank you.
@laura_barry Hello Laura, we have replied to your private message. Thank you.
@FmTbE @sduncalf fmtbe, we have sent you a private message. Thank you.
@Pdmgloria Olá P, de forma a verificar a situação, pedimos que nos indique o código da sua reserva. Por razões de segurança, solicitamos que nos envie os dados por mensagem privada. Obrigado.

@harueng_ Hello Ella, in order to verify the situation, please provide us with your booking reference or the electronic ticket number. For security reasons, please send us the information via private message. Thank you.
